### Hadith 4:565

*Narrated Zainab bint Jahsh:*

That the Prophet once came to her in a state of fear and said, "None has
the right to be worshipped but Allah. Woe unto the Arabs from a danger
that has come near. An opening has been made in the wall of Gog and
Magog like this," making a circle with his thumb and index finger.
Zainab bint Jahsh said, "O Allah's Apostle! Shall we be destroyed even
though there are pious persons among us?" He said, "Yes, when the evil
person will increase."

